msgid "Diplomacy"
msgstr "Diplomacia"

#: templates/condottieri_help/index.html:127
msgid ""
"Anytime while playing a game you can send \"letters\" to other players to "
"discuss with them about strategies or any other things."
msgstr ""
"En cualquier momento de una partida puedes enviar \"cartas\" a otros "
"jugadores para discutir con ellos sobre estrategias o cualquier otra cosa."

#: templates/condottieri_help/index.html:128
msgid ""
"IMPORTANT: All the messages that are sent while playing a game will be "
"deleted when this game is over. If you want to keep a copy of any given "
"message, you will have to copy the contents in any other place."
msgstr ""
"IMPORTANTE: Todos los mensajes enviados durante una partida serán eliminados "
"cuando la partida termine. Si quieres conservar una copia de algún mensaje, "
